@startuml
title 图像拼接 - 时序图

actor "操作者" as User
participant "StitchingPanel" as Panel
participant "StitchingService" as Service
participant "ProcessingQueue" as Queue
participant "ImageRegistration" as Registration
participant "ImageStitcher" as Stitcher
participant "ObservationSession" as Session
participant "ImageViewport" as View
participant "ProjectDocument" as Project

User -> Panel: 导入/选择拼接图块
Panel -> Service: addTile(frame, positionHint)
User -> Panel: 设置重叠比例和拼接模式
Panel -> Service: createJob(project)
Service --> Panel: ProcessingJob
Panel -> Queue: submit(job)
Queue -> Registration: align tiles
Registration --> Queue: tile transforms
Queue -> Stitcher: stitch(project)
Stitcher --> Queue: mosaic ImageFrame
Queue -> Service: onCompleted(job)
Service -> Project: save stitching parameters and result reference
Service -> Session: setDisplayFrame(mosaic)
Session -> View: setDisplayImage(mosaic)
View -> View: repaint mosaic + overlays

@enduml
